cs.IT, cs.DS, cs.CC, cs.CR, cs.DM. 

The paper deals with the construction of covering codes, which is a topic in information theory (cs.IT). The paper also uses techniques from combinatorics (cs.DM) and computational complexity (cs.CC) to analyze the efficiency of the construction. The paper involves the use of linear codes (cs.DS) and the proof involves a second moment method (cs.CR).
